row.process:
:SET &EXIT_KISS_OK#="1" :SET &EXIT_KISS_KO#="1" :SET &TEMPLATE_OS#="" :SET &OPTION_OVA#=0 :IF &TEMPLATE_NAME# <= " " : PRINT KO: TEMPLATE VIDE : SET &EXIT_KISS_KO#="&EXIT_KISS_KO#,TEMPLATE:VIDE" : MODIFY_STATE STATUS_TEXT="TEMPLATE:VIDE" : MODIFY_STATE RETCODE=10 :ELSE : PRINT OK: TEMPLATE: &TEMPLATE_NAME# :ENDIF
:IF &EF# <= " " : PRINT KO: EF VIDE : SET &EXIT_KISS_KO#="&EXIT_KISS_KO#,EF:VIDE" : MODIFY_STATE STATUS_TEXT="EF:VIDE" : MODIFY_STATE RETCODE=10 :ELSE : PRINT OK: EF: &EF# :ENDIF :PUBLISH &EXIT_KISS_OK#,,"TOP" :PUBLISH &EXIT_KISS_KO#,,"TOP"
